</li>
<li><p>On the Action Pane, select <strong>New</strong>, and then set the following values:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Packing profile ID:</strong> <em>Sort</em></li>
<li><strong>Description:</strong> <em>Sort</em></li>
<li><strong>Container packing policy:</strong> Leave this field blank.</li>
<li><strong>Container ID mode:</strong> <em>Auto</em></li>
